uk.ac.ed.csbe.sbsivisual.sbsiDataFormat
Interface ISBSIData

public interface ISBSIData

Interface for object model of SBSI data file. Implementing classes should be provide immutable objects to preserve data integrity. Only the header location can be mutable.

Author:
Richard Adams
